Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "CustomerClass" : {value : "ECCUSTOMER"},
}
}}}}[anchor|#_5e7ab025-020f-48d2-ab4a-18cd031cb4a4]((({S:Warn}You can find this example in the [https://github.com/Acumatica/Help-and-Training-Examples|Help-and-Training-Examples] repository on GitHub.
