| The request has been completed successfully. The response contains the requested record.
|- 
| ''401''
| [anchor|#_bbbfacf5-7f96-4556-b605-693007ff1854]
The user is not signed in to the system.
|- 
| ''403''
| [anchor|#_8ea45ac9-275e-4c50-affe-37f0e856e1c2]
The user has insufficient rights to access the Acumatica ERP form that corresponds to the entity.
