==HTTP Example==
The following request shows an example of the retrieval of <tt>StockItem</tt> records that are ''Active'' and that have been modified since the specified date.[anchor|#_95459d0e-6625-4d98-8b61-73c55e34c369]((({S:Warn}In the request example below, {{<Acumatica ERP instance URL>}} is the URL of the Acumatica ERP instance (such as ''https://my.acumatica.com/MyInstance''). You can omit the instance name in the URL (such as ''https://my.acumatica.com'') if the instance is installed in the root of the website.
