| The request has been completed successfully. The response body contains the data retrieved from the inquiry form.
|- 
| ''400''
| [anchor|#_888b27a9-3d50-4b57-92f4-3b75bc071639]
The data specified in the request is invalid.
|- 
| ''401''
| [anchor|#_312ca04c-df38-4443-a4e5-200490ed2c18]
The user is not signed in to the system.
|- 
| ''403''
| [anchor|#_99dee2af-80a4-4ab0-8ee7-77cb514a34cc]
The user has insufficient rights to access the Acumatica ERP form that corresponds to the entity.
|- 
