Host: [&lt;Acumatica ERP instance URL&gt;]/entity/Default/18.200.001/files
Accept: application/octet-stream
Content-Type: application/json
}}}}[anchor|#_cc7bed9d-514a-41c3-9c19-caec12217aa3]((({S:Warn}You can find this example in the [https://github.com/Acumatica/Help-and-Training-Examples|Help-and-Training-Examples] repository on GitHub.
